message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present you with our premium product, which I believe would significantly benefit your endeavors. Given its value and potential impact on your projects, I am offering it to you for $11000. This is a special opportunity tailored to your needs, considering the product's worth to you is $10000. I look forward to discussing how this product can contribute to your success. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you're interested in proceeding.
